火專家證明該枝手槍沒有撞針.<br />\n<br />\n3. 辯方可以要求警方監證科提供手槍上找到的指紋, 如果被屈人士在狗屋內被迫用手掂過枝槍必須事前向律師detail 報告及講出該幾名魔警的身份/編號/樣貌/身高/聲線 etc. 千萬不要在法庭上用 &quot;唔係好記得/唔清楚 &amp; 而而哦哦&quot; 這會讓法官有籍口不信任被屈市民.<br />\n<br />\n就算這只是魔警自編自導的一場戲, 以上三點也可以用來讓魔警自己淆底, 最終不了了之.<br />\n<br />\n可廣傳來讓大家知道如果發生魔警屈市民時怎樣自保."},{"pid":"904357aacabea7e301a4a0649d977655b839eb75","tid":1775112,"uid":255637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />似係俾狗陰啦 黑市買中空彈 托柒咩"},{"pid":"47e7dc4f4258e1b21aade98b6144d6d41777cf29","tid":1775112,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5be0df6cdda4b7d720465ad90a598945993663d","tid":1775112,"uid":3966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb20424ed579f36cd415ee0c1955a5120917f4e6","tid":1775112,"uid":291465,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52508870285635ba0ce4e4c021221b98852af552","tid":1775112,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"除左狗外，黑市都係用中空彈？<br />\n<br />\n有冇手足可以cap將圖出來？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:43:43.000Z","msg":"錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"打獵既大撚把人用hollow point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW乜又係你呀程生？幾時有開箱文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5db0de80b706981ae5d3b02da965010242d999","tid":1775112,"uid":278881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人記得<br />\n十月果陣曾經有流傳過會有廢槍流到示威者手上<br />\n時間點match"},{"pid":"8bc8334a53a9c89f563b64e6df0d9d08e8b10fd9","tid":1775112,"uid":41974,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1